lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"冇錢美國政府會俾埋錢好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"要還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該同香港一樣，救左你先，但錢之後要俾返"},{"pid":"d44bc753ac64a6bfa4df4fa3ecaf05c2d8ecf30f","tid":1052392,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d6973f315b5899fb759e47862a7fdbcc8be1eb4","tid":1052392,"uid":208722,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"054f6ca55f7b019f6091d77bef3e6d797e0fa602","tid":1052392,"uid":124107,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"廿一世紀流行病學最大嘅挑戰唔係突變嘅病毒，係一班為反醫學同藥廠霸權反到走火入魔，認為現代醫學等同霸權嘅傻撚Anti-vaxxers"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"老實講，我真係唔係好明點解要反疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似返左十七世紀，啲人反天花疫苗咁<br />\n話種左牛痘會變牛一樣，以鵝傳鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比喱班人搞到百鳩幾年黎都繼續因天花枉死<br />\n流感疫苗唔打都算，因為本身都係估會興邊隻<br />\n（但就算估唔中抵抗流感力都會高左）<br />\n但係德國麻診喱啲，咁多年都咁有效控制既都唔係打咩思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果一多人唔打又爆發返<br />\n我以前以為美國反智既人多，但原來全世界都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20182c14909acb1f4eb7fcecacd2c16415daae98","tid":1052392,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />破產"},{"pid":"84e0b4a0e8721c91de8a1b102344654041630ca4","tid":1052392,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: re